    "title": "Run Gemma 4 locally with OpenClaw 🦀 in 3 steps: ",
    "preview_text": "Last week, Gemma 4 was released. It's a very capable small model, so you can run it directly in your own devices. In this article, you'll learn how to run Gemma locally and connect it with OpenClaw in",
    "cover_url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HFTmuw-WQAAW3Nx.jpg",
