          "key": "5cmb9",
          "text": "Last week, Gemma 4 was released. It's a very capable small model, so you can run it directly in your own devices. In this article, you'll learn how to run Gemma locally and connect it with OpenClaw in 3 steps in just a few minutes.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": {
            "urls": [
              {
                "fromIndex": 28,
                "text": "https://ollama.com/download",
                "toIndex": 55
              }
